PN,37301
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FA study has found outright bans on
OL,8,Fsmartphones in schools could be
OL,9,Fineffective and undermine students'
OL,10,Ftrust without addressing issues of
OL,11,Fharmful online content, cyberbullying
OL,12,Fand the addictive nature of tech.
OL,14,FThe study for UCL found students,
OL,15,Fparents and teachers agreed the
OL,16,Fdevices could cause distraction and
OL,17,Fdisruption in the classroom but
OL,18,Fdisagreed on how the issue should be
OL,19,Faddressed.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FAcademics at the UCL Institute of
OL,8,FEducation teamed up with Life Lessons
OL,9,FEducation to hear the opinions of 732
OL,10,Fsecondary school students, 27
OL,11,Feducators and 41 parents.
OL,13,FThe study found:
OL,15,FStudents said phones had become an
OL,16,Fessential part of their lives, using
OL,17,Fthe devices for bus timetables,
OL,18,Fweather forecasts and homework apps.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FSmartphones also give them direct
OL,8,Faccess to support networks, and girls
OL,9,Fin particular said their smartphones
OL,10,Fhelp them feel safer when travelling
OL,11,Falone.
OL,13,FLead author Professor Jessica Ringrose
OL,14,Fat UCL Institute of Education said:
OL,15,F"The students we spoke to perceived
OL,16,Fblanket bans as punitive, rather than
OL,17,Fsupportive. They felt bans undermined
OL,18,Ftrust between them and the adults in
OL,19,Ftheir lives, who they felt
OL,20,Fmisunderstood the integral role phones
OL,21,Fplay in their day-to-day lives."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,8,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,9,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,10,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,12,FCo-author Edith Rodda, a PhD candidate
OL,13,Fat UCL Institute of Education, added:
OL,14,F"Rushed school smartphone policies
OL,15,Fthat don't consider students'
OL,16,Fperspectives, however well-intentioned
OL,17,Fthey may be, risk creating a cycle of
OL,18,Fpunishment that ultimately undermines
OL,19,Fthe policy's aims. Students inevitably
OL,20,Ffind workarounds, like breaking open
OL,21,Flockable phone pouches."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FThe report said digital technology was
OL,8,Fnow an unavoidable part of adult life,
OL,9,Fbut students felt blanket smartphone
OL,10,Fbans denied them the opportunity to
OL,11,Fpractise self-regulation and develop
OL,12,Fresponsible technology skills,
OL,13,Fincluding the informed use of AI.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FCo-author Dawn Aytoun from Life
OL,8,FLessons Education said: "Schools
OL,9,Fshould encourage students to learn,
OL,10,Funderstand and discuss the ethical,
OL,11,Frelational and political dimensions of
OL,12,Fthe digital world, as well as the
OL,13,Feconomic models that guide tech
OL,14,Fcompanies. Rushed policies that
OL,15,Fneglect pupil voice can hamper these
OL,16,Fdiscussions and leave students
OL,17,Funsupported."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FIn June, Sir Keir Starmer announced
OL,8,Funder-16s will be banned from using
OL,9,F"addictive" social media that is
OL,10,Fdetrimental to children's mental
OL,11,Fhealth and empowers bullies.
OL,13,FIn response to a public consultation
OL,14,Fon the issue, the Government also
OL,15,Fplans to go further to address other
OL,16,Fpotentially damaging features online.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FSir Keir said he would not compromise
OL,8,Fon the "safety and happiness of our
OL,9,Fchildren" as he announced children
OL,10,Funder the age of 16 will be banned
OL,11,Ffrom social media in a "big moment for
OL,12,Four country".
OL,14,FThe Government said it will also take
OL,15,F"world-leading" action on gaming and
OL,16,Flive-streaming platforms so strangers
OL,17,Fwill not be able to contact children.
OL,19,FSir Keir admitted the ban was not
OL,20,F"cost-free" as social media had
OL,21,Fbrought benefits for young people.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,374,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F373A1782904686
OL,3,CSchool smartphone bans 'overly
OL,4,Csimplistic' and undermine students'
OL,5,Ctrust
OL,7,FThe Government said powers in the
OL,8,FChildren's Wellbeing and Schools Act
OL,9,Fwill enable swift action, with
OL,10,Fsecondary legislation to be used to
OL,11,Fintroduce targeted protections without
OL,12,Fthe need for a whole new Act.
OL,14,FThis means the Government is aiming
OL,15,Ffor the first set of new regulations
OL,16,Fto be in effect by spring 2027.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/9
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
